@startuml
title Parties to a demand guarantee (tsrv)
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #F0E9E1
  BorderColor #8A6D3B
}
skinparam ArrowColor #8A6D3B
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #F0E9E1
skinparam noteBorderColor #8A6D3B

[Applicant\n(instructs, owes obligation)] as AP
[Guarantor\n(issues undertaking)] as GT
[Advising party\n(passes it on)] as AD
[Beneficiary\n(can demand payment)] as BE

AP --> GT : requests issuance
GT --> AD : tsrv.001 Undertaking Issuance
AD --> BE : tsrv.003 Issuance Notification
BE --> GT : tsrv.013 Undertaking Demand
note bottom of GT : the guarantor pays the beneficiary\non a compliant demand
@enduml
